Tirada dadka cudurka faafa ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus infection' (COVID-19) oo si weyn u kordhay Midowga Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska, 1ka Janaayo ilaa 15ka Maarso 2020
Tirada dadka soo gaaray cudurka faafa ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus infection' (COVID-19) waxay muujineysaa isbarbardhigyo u dhexeeya Midowga Yurub / Yurub iyo Midowga Ingiriiska ee ganacsiga, taas oo xaqiijinaysa in, in kasta oo dhibaatada COVID-19 ay ku jirto heerar kala duwan oo kala duwan dalalka, ay si degdeg ah u sii kordheyso adduunka oo dhan.
Sida laga soo xigtay khibradda Talyaaniga, wadamada, isbitaalada iyo xarumaha caafimaadka ee ugu xun waxay u baahan yihiin inay sii kordhiyaan diyaar garowga ay la kulmaan kororka tirada dadka qaba COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel caafimaad, gaar ahaan daryeel caafimaad oo daran.
Bishii Diseembar 31, 2019, waxaa lagu ogaaday in cudurka 'pneumonia' ee aan la garanayn uu sabab u yahay uu ka dhacay magaalada Wuhan ee Gobolka Hubei ee dalka Shiinaha.
Bishii Janaayo 9, 2020, Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Ka-hortagga Cudurrada ee Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay in cudurku uu sabab u ahaa fayraska coronavirus ee aan la garanayn isha oo hadda loo yaqaan cudurka neefsashada daran ee neefsashada daran ee coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tan iyo markaas, cudurka ka dhashay SARS-CoV-2 waxaa loo yaqaan cudurka coronavirus (COVID-19).
Natiijooyinka ayaa muujinaya in 80% dadka qaba COVID-19 ay la kulmaan cudur yar, taas oo ah infekshanka wadnaha neefsashada oo aan lahayn ama aan lahayn qandho, inta badanna ay ka bogsadaan.
Qiyaastii 14% dadka, COVID-19 waxay noqoneysaa cudur aad u daran oo u baahan sariirta, 6% dadka ayaa u baahan daaweyn aad u daran.
Qiyaastii 4% ee dadka COVID-19 u dhintay ayaa lagu qiyaasay sariiro.
Daraasaddan, waxaan tixgelinay kororka kiisaska COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo ka tirsan Midowga Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub (EU/EEA) iyo Yurub (UK) oo aan ku barbardhignay gobolka Hubei, Shiinaha.
Waxaan sidoo kale isbarbardhignaa tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee hadda jira ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo UK marka loo eego Talyaaniga waqtiga 31 Janaayo15 Maarso 2020.
Rakaabka COVID-19 ee EU/EEA iyo UK
Shiinaha kadib, COVID-19 ayaa ku faafay gobollada kale iyo habdhaqanka COVID-19 ee ka dambeeya gobollada kale ee adduunka ayaa ka dambeeyay tan dalka.
Bishii Maarso 11, 2020, Agaasimaha guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa COVID-19 ku dhawaaqay cudur caalami ah (pandemic).
Daabacaadda Eurosurveillance 2020 ee 5da Maarso, Spiteri iyo asxaabtiisu waxay ka hadleen kiisaska ugu horreeya ee COVID-19 ee Yurub sida ku cad qeexitaanka WHO.
EU/EEA, kiisaskii ugu horreeyay ayaa laga helay Faransiiska 24ka Janaayo 2020 markii dadkaasi ay ka tageen Wuhan, Gobolka Hubei, Shiinaha.
Bishii Ogosto 15, 2020, COVID-19 ayaa laga helay dhammaan 30 waddan oo ka mid ah Midowga Yurub / EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, oo inta u dhaxaysa 31 -ka Diseembar 2019 ilaa taariikhda la soo bandhigay, 39,768 kiis iyo 1,727 dhimasho, oo ay ka mid yihiin 17,750 kiis iyo 1,441 dhimasho oo ka yimid Talyaaniga oo keliya.
Tirada dadka qaba COVID-19 iyo kuwa la qabtay COVID-19 ayaa sii kordheysa
Xarunta Yurub ee Ka Hortagga iyo Xakamaynta Cudurrada (ECDC), tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo adduunka ah, oo ka imanaya warbaahinta hay'adaha sida Wasaaradda Caafimaadka Caalamiga ah, xarumaha caafimaadka ee WHO ee caalamiga ah iyo lambarrada, ayaa la cusbooneysiiyay maalin kasta saacadaha 2:00 subaxnimo.
Macluumaadkan waxaa loo adeegsaday falanqaynta COVID-19 ee EU/EEA iyo UK, marka la barbar dhigo kuwa Talyaaniga.
Iyada oo loo adeegsanayo tirakoobka tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee la daaweynayo, waxaan tirinay tirada dadka la helay COVID-19 ee la soo bandhigay 14 maalmood gudahood, waddan kasta oo ka mid ah EU/EEA iyo UK, intii u dhaxaysay 1 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Waxaan sidoo kale soo bandhignay tirada kiisaska la ogaaday ee waddan kasta iyadoo sii kordheysa 15ka Maarso 2020 saacaddii 2:00 subaxnimo marka la barbar dhigo Talyaaniga 31ka Janaayo 15ka Maarso.
Dhaqanka COVID-19 ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo UK
Tirada tirada dadka la helay COVID-19 ee 14 maalmood gudahood ee ka dhacay waddamada EU/EEA iyo UK guud ahaan waxay raacday kuwa ka dhacay Gobolka Hubei (Shiinaha) (Sawirro 1).
Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday guud ahaan, tirada dadka qaba COVID-19 waxay bilaabeen inay kor u kacaan qiyaastii 21ka Febraayo waxayna kor u kaceen qiyaastii 28ka Febraayo 2020 (July).
Tani waxay sabab u ahayd kororka degdegga ah ee ka yimid Talyaaniga, laakiin sida dhammaan dalalka kale ee EU/EEA iyo UK waxay la kulmeen koror isku mid ah oo COVID-19 ah (Covid-19).
Sawirka 2 wuxuu muujinayaa tirada dadka ku dhacay COVID-19, ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo UK marka la barbar dhigo Talyaaniga intii lagu jiray 31 Janaayo15 Maarso 2020.
Waxay muujineysaa in, 15ka Maarso saacadaha 2:00 subaxnimo, 15 dalal oo ka mid ah EU/EEA iyo UK ay la kulmeen tirada kiisaska la midka ah ee lagu sheegay Talyaaniga 3 toddobaad ka hor ama ka yar.
Natiijooyinka ayaa muujinaya in tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ay si degdeg ah u kordhayaan EU/EEA iyo UK.
Xaaladaha la ogaaday ee tirada dadka la helay COVID-19 waxay muujinayaan in cudurka uu si degdeg ah ugu sii kordhayaa wadamada oo dhan.
Tani waxay sii ahaataa mid la mid ah xitaa haddii dalalku ay haystaan heerar caafimaad oo kala duwan, iyadoo la adeegsanayo mabaadi'da kala duwan si loo go'aamiyo qofka qaba cudurka iyo sidoo kale la raacayo shuruudaha kala duwan ee go'aaminta dadka lagu baarayo COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan kordhinta tirada dadka la baaro.
Bilowgii Maarso 2020, dhakhaatiirta gobollada la xakameeyay ee Talyaaniga waxay sharaxeen xaaladda in 10% kiisaska COVID-19 ay u baahan yihiin daryeel caafimaad oo degdeg ah, wararkaana waxay sheegayaan in isbitaalada iyo qolka daryeelka caafimaad ee gobolladaasi ay buuxsameen.
Tirada dadka qaba COVID-19 ee ku jira sariiraha isbitaalka iyo/ama qolka daryeelka caafimaad ee ku jira heerarka EU/EEA waa 6% iyo 1% oo keliya, (warbixintan lama soo bandhigo).
Laakiin, waa in la ururiyaa si habboon iyadoo la raacayo xogta la soo bandhigay ee tirada dadka dhintay.
Sahankii 2010-11 ayaa muujinaya farqi weyn oo ku saabsan xaaladaha sariiraha caafimaadka ee Yurub, iyadoo Jarmalka ay ku jiraan 29.2 sariirood halka Portugal ay ku jiraan 4.2 qof 100,000 oo qof.
Tani waxay ka dhigan tahay in dalalka ay haystaan daryeel caafimaad oo ka badan ama ka yar heerka Talyaaniga (12.5 sariiro caafimaad oo adag oo aan lahayn 100,000 oo qof sanadkii 201011).
Waxyeelada ku yimaada buuxinta adeegyada caafimaadka, oo ku saleysan isbarbardhigga bukaannada COVID-19 ee sariirta ku jira ee EU / EEA iyo UK iyo sidoo kale dhibaatooyinka ay u leeyihiin baahida loo qabo sariirta caafimaadka ee adag in ka badan 90%, ayaa lagu sheegay warbixinta lixaad ee ECDC ee qiimeynta halista degdegga ah ee COVID-19.
Maaddaama ay jiraan xaalado caafimaad oo ka jira qaar ka mid ah waddamada Midowga Yurub/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, iyo in isbitaalada iyo xarumaha caafimaadka ee xoogga leh ay adeegsadaan dadka ku nool gobollada la aqoonsan yahay, macluumaadka bukaanka iyo xaaladaha caafimaadka ee xoogga leh ayaa la heli karaa iyada oo loo marayo Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Xaaladaha Talyaaniga iyo kuwa ka socda dalalka kale waxay muujinayaan in dhibaatada COVID-19 COVID-19 ay si degdeg ah ugu sii kordheyso EU/EEA iyo UK.
Sidaa darteed, isbitaalada iyo xarumaha caafimaadka ee ugu muhiimsan waa inay diyaar u noqdaan xaaladaha faafa ee SARS-CoV-2 ee dadka deegaanka iyo kororka tirada dadka qaba COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel caafimaad, gaar ahaan daryeel caafimaad oo aad u daran, sida xaaladaha ku jira qaybaha ka soo horjeeda Talyaaniga.
Sida laga soo xigtay falanqaynta degdegga ah ee ECDC, diyaarinta degdegga ah ee saxda ah ayaa muhiim u ah ka hortagga faafitaanka SARS-COV-2, iyadoo la tixgelinayo in laga hortago faafitaanka faafitaanka si loo bogsiiyo, maadaama kororka degdegga ah ee tirada bukaanka la filayo ay u adkeyn karto maamulka iyo isbitaalada inay helaan waqti ku filan si ay u ogaadaan, u aqbalaan oo ay u hirgeliyaan hababka loo baahan yahay haddii aan la fulin waqti ka hor.
Baaritaanka degdegga ah ee dhibaatada ayaa muujinaya siyaabo caafimaad oo lagu xakameynayo dhibaatada dhibaatada.
Waxaa jira heerar yar oo ay dalalku awood u leeyihiin inay kor u qaadaan awoodooda si loo yareeyo faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyo in la yareeyo cadaadiska caafimaadka.
Haddii ay taasi fashilantay, waxaa la filayaa in daryeelka caafimaadka ee dalalka kale ee EU/EEA ay ku adkeysan doonaan tirada sii kordheysa ee bukaanka u baahan daryeel caafimaad oo xooggan maalmaha ama toddobaadyada soo socda.
Cudurka Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), oo ah sababta ugu weyn ee cudurka neefsashada daran ee daran (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ayaa dilay in ka badan 3,000 oo qof iyo in ka badan 80,000 oo qof ayaa hadda laga helay Shiinaha iyo meelo kale oo adduunka ah, taasoo keentay masiibo aadanaha.
Sida fayraska SARS-CoV, oo sababiyay SARS kumanaan qof sanadkii 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ayaa sidoo kale la kala saari karaa cudurka iyo waxay keentaa calaamado isku mid ah.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, COVID-19 ma aha mid aad u daran sida SARS oo ay u dileyso dad yar laakiin waxay u badan tahay inay la wareegto oo ay saameyn ku yeelato ragga waaweyn iyo ragga ka badan dhalinyarada iyo dumarka.
Iyada oo la jawaabayo warbaahinta badankood ee ku saabsan cudurrada shilku, boggan waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu muujiyo dib u eegis dhammaystiran oo ku saabsan cilmi baarista shilku.
Waxaan ka hadli doonaa waxyaabaha aasaasiga ah ee cudurrada, sababta, fayraska, baaritaanka, daaweynta, saadaasha, iyo ka hortagga.
Inkastoo su'aalo badan ay weli u baahan yihiin jawaab, waxaan rajeyneynaa in falanqayntaani ay caawin doonto fahamka iyo xallinta cudurkan walaacsan ee aadanaha.
Xaflada gu'ga ee Janaayo 25, 2020 waxay noqotay xaflad aan la iloobin oo loogu talagalay Shiinaha oo lagu baaqay inay guryahooda joogaan fasaxyada iyo toddobaadyada soo socda sababtoo ah faafitaanka cudurka aan la aqoon ee cusub.
Fayraska ayaa si buuxda u la mid ahaa coronavirus (CoV) oo keenta cudurka neefsashada daran ee daran (SARS) sanadkii 2003; sidaa darteed, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) wuxuu ugu magac daray SARS-CoV-2 11ka Febraayo 2020, waxaana cudurka uu keeno loo magacaabay Cudurka COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Cudurka ayaa ka bilaabmay Wuhan, Shiinaha, isla markaana si dhakhso leh u faafay dalka oo dhan iyo qiyaastii 50 dal oo kale oo adduunka ah.
Bishii Maarso 2, 2020, fayraska ayaa sababay in ka badan 80,000 oo qof oo la xaqiijiyay inay qabaan COVID-19, in ka badan 40,000 ayaa ka badbaaday iyo in ka badan 3,000 ayaa dhintay.
WHO waxay ka digtay in COVID-19 uu yahay cadowga ugu weyn ee aadanaha iyo inuu ka khatar badan yahay argagixisada.
Sida laga soo xigtay PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), in ka yar laba bilood, in ka badan 200 oo warqadood ayaa lagu daabacay COVID-19 oo ay ku jiraan cudurka faafa, cudurka, sababaha, baaritaanka iyo daaweynta laga soo bilaabo warbixintii ugu horreysay ee Janaayo 7, 2020 oo lagu ogaaday hiddaha fayraska oo laga soo saaray cudurrada kala duwan.
Cilmi-baarista ayaa lagu wadaa in lagu dabaqo cilmi-baarista ka dhacday garoonka cusub ee xawaaraha sare leh.
Marka ugu horreysa, waxaan isku dayi doonaa inaan isbarbardhigno COVID-19 iyo SARS iyo cudurrada kale ee COVID, cudurka neefsashada ee Bariga Dhexe (MERS, 2012).
Waxa kale oo aan ka wada hadli doonaa waxa aan ka baranay sidii looga hortagi lahaa cudurkaas iyo su'aalaha aan weli la jawaabin.
CoVs waxaa loo tixgeliyaa inay yihiin fayraska ugu nugul ee aadanaha, oo keena qiyaastii 15% ka mid ah cudurrada hargabka ee caadiga ah 4.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, qarnigii, waxaan helnay laba jeer oo ugu khatarta badan ee COVID-19 ee aadanaha, kuwaas oo ah SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV, oo ka dhashay cudurrada ugu horreeya Shiinaha 2003 iyo Sacuudi Carabiya 2012, si dhakhso leh u faafay dalalka kale oo ay ku faaftay cudurrada iyo dhimashada tiro badan.
Sidaa darteed, COVID-19 ee hadda jira waa COVID-19 ee saddexaad ee ugu badan ee ka soo baxda taariikhda aadanaha ee la yaqaan.
Sida lagu muujiyey Sawirka. Sawirka.1,1, cudurrada hargabka ee aan la garanayn asalkoodu ayaa markii ugu horreysay lagu soo wargeliyay Wuhan bishii Diseembar 31, 2019 Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka Shiinaha.
Toddoba maalmood ka dib, koontada CoV ayaa la soo saaray.
Bishii Janaayo 15, 2020 waxaa la sheegay in Wuhan ay tahay magaalada ugu horeysa ee laga soo qaato cudurka.
Waqtigan xaadirka ah, cudurka ayaa si degdeg ah ugu faafay magaalooyinka hareeraha ah iyo dalalka.
