Bukaanka qaba dhibaatooyinka neefsashada ee daran waxay u baahan yihiin caawimaad oksijiin-ka-xidhka jirka (ECMO), oo ah habka lagu daaweeyo dadka si buuxda u neefsashada u fashilmay oo u horseeda dhimashada.
Xakamaynta heerarka elektrolyte, ka hortagga iyo daaweynta fayraska kale ee ku dhaca fayraska iyo cudurka faafa, iyo ilaalinta xubnaha jirka ee muhiimka ah ee la shaqeeya ayaa muhiim u ah cudurka SARS-CoV-2.
Waxaa la ogaaday in duufaanta cytokine ay ka timaado cudurka hargabka si ay u soo saarto falcelin badan oo ka timaada nidaamka difaaca jirka ee bukaanka qaba SARS iyo MERS.
Cytokine storm waa falcelin jirka ah oo ku saabsan soo saarista cytokines kala duwan oo ay ku jiraan TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, iyo MCP-1.
Cytokines-yada ayaa ka dhigaya in unugyada difaaca ee jirka ay soo saaraan unugyo badan oo ah sababaha ugu waaweyn ee ay u dhacaan ARDS iyo jirka.
Hoos u dhigista cayilka waa mid muhiim u ah daaweynta duufaannada cytokine, gaar ahaan bukaannada daran.
Corticosteroids iyo tocilizumab, oo ah anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, ayaa loo isticmaalay daaweynta duufaanta cytokine.
