Si ka duwan SARS, dadka qaba MERS ayaa sidoo kale la kulmay cillad xidid ah, oo hadda ah MERS oo keliya cudurrada HCoV ay keenaan.
In ka badan 30% dadka qaba cudurka ayaa qaba dhibaatooyinka cudurka, sida cudurka qanjirka iyo qanjirka.
