Tirada dhimashada COVID-19 waxay noqon kartaa mid aad u sarreysa sababtoo ah waxaa laga yaabaa inaysan jirin dad aan la hubin - tusaale ahaan guriga, guryaha daryeelka dadka waayeelka ah, iyo meelo kale.
Xogta ku saabsan qeybta Talyaaniga ayaa lagu ogaaday in tirada dhimashada inta lagu jiro xilliyada weerarka ay ka badan tahay tirada rasmiga ah ee COVID oo ah 4-5 jeer tirada.
Afhayeenka Xarumaha Xakamaynta iyo Ka Hortagga Cudurrada ee Mareykanka (CDC) ayaa qirtay in "Waxaan ognahay in [tirada dhimashada] aysan sax ahayn", taas oo aan xaqiijinay iyo in aan u sheegnay dadka Mareykanka.
