Shabakadaha neerfaha ee loo yaqaan 'artificial intelligence-based convolutional neural networks' ayaa loo qaabeeyey inay ku xakameynayaan sawirada fayraska iyagoo adeegsanaya sawirada Xaysinta iyo CT.
