Dhamaadkii 1990-meeyadii iyo qarnigii 21-aad, gacmaha lagu nadiifiyo (oo sidoo kale lagu magacaabo gacmaha lagu nadiifiyo khamriga, gacmaha lagu nadiifiyo cudurka cudurka) ayaa caan ku noqday.
Inta badan waxaa laga sameeyaa isopropyl alcohol ama ethanol oo lagu daro walxaha adag sida Carbomer (polymer of acrylic acid) si ay u noqdaan kuwo dabiici ah, ama humectant sida glycerin si ay u noqdaan biyo, ama daabacaad si loo fududeeyo dadka isticmaala iyo hoos u dhigista cabitaanka khamriga.
Isku darista hydrogen-peroxide-ka la isku daray waxay kordhisaa awoodda ay u leedahay inay u dileyso bakteeriyada.
Daawooyinka daawooyinka khamriga ah waxay dilaan bakteeriyada, bakteeriyada u adkaysta daawooyinka badan (MRSA iyo VRE), cudurka shubanka, iyo fayrasyada qaarkood (oo ay ku jiraan HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccina, influenza, iyo hepatitis) iyo fangaska.
