Xiddiga angiotensin-beddelaya enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa xiddiga ugu sarreeya ee ku xiran (bararka unugyada) unugyada, neerfaha, wadnaha, saliidda, iyo unugyada.
ACE2 waxay ka hortagtaa waxqabadka angiotensin-beddelaya enzyme (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa heerarka angiotensin-II iyadoo kordhineysa Ang(1-7) si ay u sameyso daawo lagu daaweyn karo cudurada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sidii horudhac u ah in la soo galo cudurrada coronavirus qaarkood.
Dadka waxaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Xiddiga angiotensin-beddelaya enzyme 2 waxaa ku jira zinc oo ah metaloenzyme laga helo dusha sare ee unugyada dhiigga iyo unugyada kale.
Protein ACE2 wuxuu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waxay ku dhex dhacdaa maqaarka jirka hal mar, iyadoo waxyaabaha ugu muhiimsan ay ka muuqdaan dusha sare ee subagga ee unugyada iyo unugyada kale.
Goobta ugu sareysa ee ACE2 waxaa laga saaraa maqaarka oo loo wareejiyaa xeryahooda sheddase, ka dibna biyaha borotiinka ah ee soo baxa waxaa loo wareejiyaa dhiigga oo loo beddelaa saliid.
ACE2 waxaa laga helaa inta badan xubnaha jirka: ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay maqaarka unugyada, gaar ahaan unugyada nooca II ee la soo saaray ee derbiyada sanbabada, unugyada yaryar ee unugyada, neerfaha iyo unugyada dhiigga, iyo unugyada unugyada unugyada ee ku jira inta badan xubnaha jirka.
