ACE waxay ku xiran tahay hormoonka angiotensin I ee angiotensin II.
ACE2 wuxuu ku dhejiyaa carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine oo ka soo jeeda angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) wuxuuna ku wareegayaa angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale la qabsan kartaa silsilado kala duwan oo ay ku jiraan [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa wareegga maqaarka ee u gudbiya amino acid neutral SLC6A19 waxaana la rumeysan yahay inay sabab u tahay cudurka Hartnup.
Marka borotiinka lagu wareejiyo maqaarka, ACE2 wuxuu u dhaqmaa sidii albaabada ugu weyn ee loo galo bakteeriyada fayraska qaar ka mid ah coronaviruses, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirnaanta borotiinka spike S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee ACE2 ee ugu weyn ee ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada waxay keentaa in fayraska iyo unugyada ay ka soo baxaan booskooda oo ay ku noqdaan dhismaha unugyada.
Nidaamkan soo gelitaanka wuxuu sidoo kale u baahan yahay in la ogaado borotiinka S iyo serine protease TMPRSS2, oo la wareejiyo si loo hubiyo in la isticmaalo daaweynta. Tani waxay keentay in qaar ka mid ah ay u maleynayaan in yareynta heerarka ACE2, ee unugyada, ay ka caawin karto la dagaalanka cudurka.
