WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday 11kii Febraayo 2020 in magaca rasmiga ah ee cudurka loo magacaabo "COVID-19".
Agaasimaha WHO Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ayaa sharaxay in CO ay matalaan coronavirus, VI ay matalaan virus, D inay matalaan cudur, iyo 19 markii cudurka la ogaaday markii ugu horreysay: 31 December 2019.
Magaca waxaa loo doortay si looga fogaado in lagu xuso meel kasta (sida Shiinaha), noocyada xayawaanka ama kooxda dadka, iyadoo la raacayo xulashada caalamiga ah si looga fogaado takoorka. Fayraska keena COVID-19 waxaa loo yaqaan cudurka neefsashada daran ee xanuunka daran ee coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
