Waxaa jira saddex nooc oo ka mid ah daawooyinka ka hortagga cudurka.
Marka hore, cilmi baarayaashu waxay rabaan inay sameeyaan daawo ka hortag ah fayraska.
Isticmaalka fayraska noocaas ah, ma aha mid nool ama dhintay, wuxuu ujeedkiisu yahay inuu abuuro hab-dhaqanka jirka ee jirka ee cudurrada cusub iyo COVID-19.
Qaab kale oo loo yaqaan 'subunit vaccines', ayaa ah in la sameeyo daawo ka hortag ah oo ka hortagta unugyada jirka si ay u difaacaan bakteeriyada jirka.
SARS-CoV-2, daraasadu waxay ku saabsan tahay borotiinka S-spike ee caawiya fayraska inuu galo ACE2 enzyme receptor.
Qaabka saddexaad waa tallaalka nucleic acid (DNA ama RNA vaccines, habka cusub ee loo abuuro tallaalka antibodies).
Tijaabada tallaalka ee laga soo saaro nidaamyadan waxay u baahan doonaan tijaabooyin caafimaad oo caafimaad oo la xaqiijin karo. Bishii Maarso 16, 2020, tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee ugu horreeya ayaa la bilaabay afar qof oo iskaa wax u qabso ah oo tijaabooyin ah ku sameeyay Seattle.
Daawooyinka xakameynta waxay ku jiraan koodhka hidde-gelinta ee aan waxyeello lahayn ee laga soo saaray fayraska cudurka. Kor u qaadista nidaamka difaaca jirka ayaa la sheegay inay ku adag tahay in la sameeyo daawooyinka xakameynta SARS-COV-2, laakiin tani waa khiyaamo.
Ilaa iyo bishii Abriil 2020, waxaa jira in ka badan 300 tijaabooyin caafimaad oo la sameeyay.
Toddoba tijaabooyin ayaa ahaa tijaabooyin lagu qiimeeyay daawooyin hore loo ansixiyay in lagu daaweeyo hargabka, oo ay ku jiraan afar tijaabo oo lagu qiimeeyay hydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Daawooyinka jeermiska ee loo isticmaalo daaweynta cudurrada kale ayaa ah kuwa ugu weyn ee ka qaybqaata cilmi baarista Shiinaha, oo ay ku jiraan sagaal tijaabo oo heerka III ah oo ka socda remdesivir oo ka socda dhowr dal oo ay soo saareen warbixin dhamaadka Abriil.
