Cilmi-baarista ugu dambeysa waxay muujineysaa in qiyaaso badan oo ribavirin ah loo baahan yahay si looga hortago SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoxanide ayaa lagu taageeray in la sii wado cilmi baarista noolaha ka dib markii la muujiyey daciifnimo ku saabsan horumarinta SARS- CoV-2. Natiijooyinka ayaa muujinaya in protein-ka ugu horreeya ee spike ee transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) uu muhiim u yahay soo-gelinta SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo la isku xiro ACE2 receptor.
Cilmi-baarista chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo ay ku jiraan ama aan lahayn azithromycin waxay leedahay daciifnimo badan oo ka hortagtay dhakhaatiirta inay aqbalaan isticmaalka daaweynta iyada oo aan la helin baaritaan dheeri ah. Oseltamivir ma xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro oo faa'iidooyinkeedu lama oga COVID-19.
Duufaanta cytokine waxay noqon kartaa mid aad u daran marka COVID-19 ay dhacdo.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine ay leedahay sifooyinka anti-cytokine storm. Tocilizumab waxaa lagu soo bandhigay nidaamka caafimaadka ee Shirkadda Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha kadib markii la sameeyay baaritaano yar.
Waa heerka 2aad ee tijaabada diyaarinta heer qaran ee Talyaaniga ka dib markii ay muujisay calaamadaha cudurka ee dadka aan la aqoon.
Waxaa hadda lagu daraa baaritaanka dhiigga serum ferritin si loo ogaado duufaannada cytokine, waxaana la filayaa in ay bilaabaan waxyaabo la mid ah, kuwaas oo la rumeysan yahay inay dilaan bukaanno qaarkood.
Khilaafka soo-saaraha ee Interleukin-6 waxaa ansixiyay FDA iyadoo lagu saleynayo daraasado hore oo lagu daaweynayo cudurka sii deynta cytokine ee loo yaqaan 'steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome' oo ay keento waxyaabo kale, CAR T cell therapy, sanadkii 2017.
Ilaa hadda, ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo xaqiiqo ah in dhakhtarku uusan ku daaweyn karin CRS.
Isbedelka jirka ee ka soo horjeeda jirka ee la sameeyay iyo isku darka ka soo horjeeda jirka ee ka badbaaday COVID-19 oo lagu daro dadka u baahan waa arrin lagu eedeeyay inay tahay habka ugu horreeya ee cudurka ka dhaca marka aan la tijaabin.
