Habab kale oo kale, sida cytotoxicity-ka unugyada antibody-ku xiran iyo/ama phagocytosis, waa suurtagal.
Nidaam kale oo lagu daaweynayo ciidamada ka hortagga cudurrada cudurka ayaa la sameynayaa, tusaale ahaan, adeegsiga ciidamada ka hortagga cudurrada monoclonal.
Wax soo saarka serum convalescent, oo ka kooban dhiig ka soo baxay bukaanno bogsaday iyo ciidamada ka shaqeeya la dagaalanka cudurrada fayraska, ayaa lagu dari karaa si loo kordhiyo wax soo saarka daawada.
